  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automated account warm-up (scroll, like, follow) on real iPhones",
    "Scheduled auto-posting to TikTok and Instagram",
    "One Mac drives 10+ iPhones simultaneously, up to 8 accounts per platform per iPhone",
    "Cloud Drop: queue content from any device for your Mac to post",
    "Crash recovery and auto-resume with no double-posts",
    "Data stays local on your Mac",
